Good Morning World!

40
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:36,910
Good Morning World!

41
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:41,000
Rid away the impossibility of the dark

42
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:46,350
An odyssey turning mythology
into the everyday

43
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:55,760
In this painstaking journey,
turning over every stone

44
00:03:56,240 --> 00:04:00,680
We'll expand our world

45
00:04:15,510 --> 00:04:17,900
Senku!

46
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:20,610
Answer me!

47
00:04:20,610 --> 00:04:22,820
