59
00:05:10,170 --> 00:05:12,410
I'd have to kill you, too.

60
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:15,330
Please don't lose your head.

61
00:05:38,690 --> 00:05:39,940
Taiju-kun!

62
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:43,690
Don't worry, Yuzuriha.

63
