few animals that use tools.

226
00:19:51,290 --> 00:19:56,090
Crows, otters, and orangutans, for example.

227
00:19:56,740 --> 00:20:02,090
But there's only one
species that uses science.

228
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:07,060
