the universe has to offer.

233
00:21:01,950 --> 00:21:03,980
I'm the master of science!

234
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:49,990
I guess I haven't introduced myself yet.

235
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:52,690
Nice to meet you.

236
00:21:54,610 --> 00:21:56,170
