240
00:22:07,630 --> 00:22:10,260
Acquired Food,
Clothing and Shelter!!

241
00:22:11,020 --> 00:22:14,650
I'm going to build a technological
civilization from scratch,

242
00:22:15,210 --> 00:22:18,350
