00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:55,780
In my hands awakens

247
00:22:55,780 --> 00:22:57,220
The passion overflowing

248
00:22:57,220 --> 00:22:59,730
Just wandering through this world

249
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,860
Your one shining pure

250
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:03,740
Could never be pierced
